message: "If you use Open Agent Commerce, please cite it as below."
title: "Open Agent Commerce: protocols and reference primitives for agent-mediated commerce"
abstract: >-
  Open protocols and reference primitives that let AI agents create accounts,
  authorize spend, receive credentials, and prove ownership under signed,
  revocable user consent with a tamper-evident provenance trail, and a Unified
  Agent Protocol that normalizes Visa TAP, Google AP2, and Stripe/OpenAI ACP into
  one verifiable request.
